if mapDevice > 0 then EntityInteraction(mapDevice) Wait(6000) end

if portal > 0 then EntityInteraction(portal) Wait(6000) end

--todo: make this func work for any hideout currentMap = GetNumberedAreaName()
while currentMap == "HideoutTemplarLab" do EntityInteraction(portal) Wait(3000) currentMap = GetNumberedAreaName() end
